          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾蒙宠眷，六宫无比，只怕日久恩疏，难免白首之叹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二郎神） 提起便心痛，念寒微侍夜廷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更依傍辇多荣幸。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论恩情，若得个久长时，死也幸。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "断肠枉泣红颜命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李隆基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤与你好似比目之鱼，爱妃何必多虑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨玉环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既蒙陛下如此情浓，趁此双星之下，乞赐盟约，一见始终。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李隆基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此香案伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨玉环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众内监、众宫女同设罢。〖吹打〗。牛郎、织女同上，同上桌子。百鸟彩切托明月。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨玉环 （同猫儿坠） 香肩斜靠，携手下阶行，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一片因何当殿横，罗衣陡觉夜凉生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨玉环",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愿得你我福寿齐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李隆基",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在地同为连理枝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨玉环",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天长地久情无尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李隆基",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此誓绵绵永佳期。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李隆基、杨玉环同拜，同起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨玉环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾感陛下今夕之盟，死生守之矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李隆基 （猫儿坠） 喜今夕同把心结，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨玉环 （猫儿坠） 问今夜有谁折证？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众內监、众宫女引李隆基、杨玉环同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "牛郎 （猫儿坠） 只见他盟誓密，此拜祷孜孜，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两情洽无二意，同一词。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨玉环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天孙，你看唐天子与贵妃，好不恩爱也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猫儿坠） 俏相偎倚着香肩没些缝儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨玉环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我与你既缔天上良缘，当做情场管领，况二人向我等说誓，须当保护。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猫儿坠） 见了他恋比翼慕并枝，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "合令他长作人间风月司。"
        },
        {
          "character": "织女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是他二人劫难将至，免不得生离死别，若果后来不能背今盟，决当为之管合。"
        },
        {
          "character": "牛郎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天孙之言有理。你看夜色将阑，且回斗牛宫去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "织女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "织女 （同猫儿坠） 天上留佳会，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年年在斯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情缘顷刻时。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（牛郎、织女相扶下。）"
        }
      ],
